[h4 
	" 099-000
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Fighting is needed in the tight corridors of the castle.
	$LF
	"I dodge when I can and setup fights out of my walking path when possible.
	$LF
	"The yellow guys can be held in place since they always try to go straight for the king and this game has no pathing.
	$LF
	"The green guys are weaker to soldiers than knights. 
	$LF
	"I kill the enemy king with my king because all my closer troops were failing.
	$LF
